import React, { Fragment } from 'react';
import { Segment, Button, Placeholder, Card } from 'semantic-ui-react';
const AffilieListItemPlaceholder = () => {
  return (


    <Card.Group doubling itemsPerRow={3} stackable>
  <Card>
   
      <Placeholder>
        <Placeholder.Image square />
      </Placeholder>
    

    <Card.Content>

        <Placeholder>
          <Placeholder.Header>
            <Placeholder.Line length='very short' />
            <Placeholder.Line length='medium' />
          </Placeholder.Header>
          <Placeholder.Paragraph>
            <Placeholder.Line length='short' />
          </Placeholder.Paragraph>
        </Placeholder>
      
    </Card.Content>

  </Card>
)
</Card.Group> 

/*     <Fragment>

                <Placeholder.Line />
                <Placeholder.Line />
              </Placeholder.Header>
              <Placeholder.Paragraph>
                <Placeholder.Line />
              </Placeholder.Paragraph>
            </Placeholder>
          </Segment>
          <Segment>
            <Placeholder>
              <Placeholder.Line />
              <Placeholder.Line />
            </Placeholder>
          </Segment>
          <Segment secondary style={{ minHeight: 70 }} />
          <Segment clearing>
            <Button disabled color='blue' floated='right' content='View' />

        </Segment.Group>

    </Fragment> */
  );
};
export default AffilieListItemPlaceholder;
